! XML Language Support

Provides syntax highlighting for XML and SVG in code blocks.

!! Supported Content

* Fenced code blocks: ```` ```xml ```` or ```` ```svg ````
* Typed blocks: `$$$.xml` or `$$$.svg`
* Tiddlers with type `text/xml` or `image/svg+xml`

!! Features

* XML/SVG syntax highlighting with tag and attribute coloring
* Bracket matching for tags
* Code folding for nested elements
